Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on POS tagging for code-mixed social media text. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed approach uses Recurrent Neural Network (RNN) architecture, which is a popular machine learning technique for NLP tasks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes an AI-based approach for POS tagging code-mixed social media text. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses RNN-LM architecture, which is a type of neural network. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with processing and analyzing text data, which is relevant to information retrieval tasks.
